"><div class="media-object-video"><div class="wsj-media-summary clearfix"><div class="strap-container"><h4 class="strap" itemprop="description"></h4></div></div><iframe width="400" height="225" src="https://video-api.wsj.com/api-video/player/v3/iframe.html?guid=63F74051-DE2F-4EC0-A40C-661F43B17EE4&amp;height=225&amp;width=400&amp;plid=video_amp&amp;chainVideos=true&amp;parentUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2Fonly-biden-can-elect-trump-hunter-joe-irs-justice-2024-investigation-2f02c2cb&amp;a=a" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></iframe><p class="imageCaption">仙境。随着共和党总统候选人开始提供比唐纳德·特朗普的各种回报更多的东西，拜登总统认为，反对“MAGA”是他通往第二任期的道路。图片：美联社/盖蒂图片社 综合：马克·凯利<span class="imageCredit">华尔街日报互动版</span></p></div></div></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Tue, 25 Jul 2023 22:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/only-biden-can-elect-trump-hunter-joe-irs-justice-2024-investigation-2f02c2cb</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/only-biden-can-elect-trump-hunter-joe-irs-justice-2024-investigation-2f02c2cb<category> 2024 年选举</category><category>拜登家族</category><category>税务欺诈</category><category>国税局</category><category>举报人</category><category>检控</category><category>司法部</category><category>企业/行业新闻</category><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>犯罪/法律诉讼</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论/意见</category><category>法激活过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>唐纳德·特朗普</category><category>公司的</category><category>行业新闻</category><category>政治的</category><category>一般新闻</category><category>犯罪</category><category>合法举动</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论</category><category>意见</category><category>法蒂瓦过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category></item></channel></rss>